50|$|Michel Lotito (June 15, 1950June 25, 2007) was a French entertainer, born in Grenoble, {{famous for}} {{deliberately}} consuming indigestible objects. He {{came to be}} known as Monsieur <b>Mangetout</b> ("Mr Eat-All").|$|E
